<title>USA: Bombay Co Q1 net loss widens.</title>
<headline>Bombay Co Q1 net loss widens.</headline>
<dateline>FORT WORTH, Texas 1997-05-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>1997			1996</p>
<p> Shr loss		   $0.12     loss	 $0.06</p>
<p> Net loss		   4,625     loss	 2,440</p>
<p> Net sales		 67,231		   68,082</p>
<p> Avg shrs		  38,022		   38,198</p>
<p>(All data above 000s except per share numbers)</p>
<p>NOTES: The quarters ended May 3, 1997 and May 4, 1996.</p>
<p>1996 results include $835,000 after-tax gain from accounting change. Loss excluding gain amounted to $3.3 million or $0.08 per share.</p>
